      "content": "That's a solid start, really hits the atmosphere. To make it even more visceral, I want to add some character elements to the scene. Can you describe the people you might see loitering on these street corners or hanging out in these alleys? I want to make sure the reader gets a clear sense of the types of people who inhabit this area so the tension feels real.",
